org.cloudgraph.rdb.graph

Class ParallelSubgraphTask

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cloudgraph.store.lang.AssemblerSupport
      • org.cloudgraph.rdb.graph.ParallelSubgraphTask
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SubgraphTask

    public class ParallelSubgraphTask
extends AssemblerSupport
implements SubgraphTask
    A concurrent task which processes a portion of a data graph or sub-graph while leveraging shared resources, such as the data graph being assembled and the thread pool, through the shared parent ParallelGraphAssembler.
    Since:
    0.6.2
    Author:
    Scott Cinnamond
    See Also:
    ParallelGraphAssembler, LangStoreGraphAssembler
